{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_compliance_rules_doc", "label": "COMPLIANCE.md \u2014 Reglas de Contenido M\u00e9dico como C\u00f3digo", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Fuente de verdad: cada regla documentada aqu\u00ed debe tener contraparte implementada en c\u00f3digo, y una regla nueva se agrega primero aqu\u00ed. Son reglas duras que bloquean el pipeline, no sugerencias de estilo."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_personal_attributes", "label": "NO_PERSONAL_ATTRIBUTES (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe segunda persona + condici\u00f3n/s\u00edntoma o asumir que el lector padece algo (ej. '\u00bfSufres de migra\u00f1as?'); permite cifras poblacionales y contenido educativo neutro."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_diagnostic_language", "label": "NO_DIAGNOSTIC_LANGUAGE (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe 'diagnostica', 'cura', 'trata', 'elimina' como promesa del servicio y cualquier diagn\u00f3stico por redes; el contenido educativo debe cerrar con derivaci\u00f3n a consulta presencial."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_guaranteed_claims", "label": "NO_GUARANTEED_CLAIMS (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe 'garantizado', '100% efectivo', 'resultados inmediatos', 'cl\u00ednicamente probado' sin evidencia citable; permite 'estudios sugieren que\u2026' con fuente en el copy."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_before_after", "label": "NO_BEFORE_AFTER (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe transformaciones antes/despu\u00e9s incluso impl\u00edcitas (Meta 2026), ej. persona 'luciendo saludable' junto al servicio como resultado."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_remote_diagnosis", "label": "NO_REMOTE_DIAGNOSIS (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe ofrecer evaluaci\u00f3n/diagn\u00f3stico por DM o comentarios y contenido que sustituya la consulta; permite llamados a agendar consulta presencial."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_misleading_testimonials", "label": "NO_MISLEADING_TESTIMONIALS (blocker)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe testimonios de pacientes (reales o inventados) como evidencia de resultados; permite cifras poblacionales de fuentes p\u00fablicas (MINSAL, OMS) citadas."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_no_fear_urgency", "label": "NO_FEAR_URGENCY (warning)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe apelar al miedo o urgencia artificial ('No esperes a que sea tarde'); permite llamados a la acci\u00f3n neutros como 'Agenda tu control anual'."}, {"id": "docs_compliance_required_educational_disclaimer", "label": "REQUIRED_EDUCATIONAL_DISCLAIMER (warning, regla positiva)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/COMPLIANCE.md", "source_location": "## Reglas", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "